{"lemma":"غَفْلَة","slug":"غَفْلَة","root":"غ.ف.ل","root_slug":"غ-ف-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ف-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"غَفْلَة","root":"غفل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adv","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32130","n32139","n32140"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"neglect"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"carelessness, heedlessness","examples":[{"text":"فِي غَفْلَة","english":"in heedlessness, heedlessly"},{"text":"ٱقْتَرَبَ لِلنَّاسِ حِسَابُهُمْ وَهُمْ فِى غَفْلَةٍۢ مُّعْرِضُونَ","english":"The time of people’s judgment has drawn near, yet they are heedlessly turning away."}]},{"pos":"adv","gloss":"suddenly, surprisingly, unexpectedly","examples":[{"text":"يَأْتِي المَوْتُ غَفْلَةً","english":"Death comes unexpectedly"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun from the verb غَفَلَ (ḡafala, “to become heedless”).\n\nAdverbial accusative of غَفْلَة (ḡafla, “heedlessness”)."},"ipa":["/ɣaf.la/","/ɣaf.la.tan/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32130","headword_ar":"غفّلهُ","root":"gfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tagofiylN","text_ar":"تَغْفِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to become unmindful, forgetful, neglectful, heedless,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inadvertent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  See also 4. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~agofiylu","text_ar":"التَّغْفِيلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [also]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sufficing"},{"kind":"text","text":"one's companion ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of an affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he who is the object thereof is unmindful, unoccupied"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"actually,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by anything."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, K, TA.) [You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gf~l SaAHibahu","text_ar":"غفّل صَاحِبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sufficed his companion in respect of an affair when he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the latter)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was unmindful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gf~lhu","text_ar":"غفّلهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, O, K, but in my copy of the Mgh written without tesh-deed,) inf. n. as above, (O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He concealed it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, O, K,) namely, a thing. (Mgh, O.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n32139","headword_ar":"غَفْلَةٌ","root":"gfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"the subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gafala","text_ar":"غَفَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISd, K,) or it is an inf. n. (S, O, Msb, TA) and also a simple subst., (TA,) or the subst. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gafalapN","text_ar":"غَفَلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"f","text_ar":"ف"},{"kind":"text","text":"to distinguish it from the inf. n.; (Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gafalN","text_ar":"غَفَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISd, K,) or this may be the inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gafila","text_ar":"غَفِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", mentioned above as a dial. var. outweighed in authority; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gufolaAnN","text_ar":"غُفْلَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or this may be an inf. n. like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuforaAnN","text_ar":"كُفْرَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and it may be a simple subst.; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Unmindfulness, forgetfulness, neglectfulness, heedlessness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inadvertence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K;) [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state in which is"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"absence of a thing from the mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man; and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unmindfulness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forgetfulness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intentional neglect:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gafolapN","text_ar":"غَفْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forgetting, neglecting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being unmindful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing: (Abu-l-Bakà, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"want of requisite knowledge"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cognizance"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing: (El-Harállee, TA:) or, accord. to Er-Raghib,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"negligence occurring from littleness of consideration and of vigilance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as some say, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"following the soul in that which it desires,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY gafolapK","text_ar":"فِى غَفْلَةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In a state of unmindfulness"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano gafolapK","text_ar":"عَنْ غَفْلَةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in consequence of unmindfulness"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., may often be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at unawares."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["ISd","K","S","O","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n32140","headword_ar":"غَفَلَةٌ","root":"gfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}